definitions.definition: To manually load or unload a container , trailer , or to otherwise manually move bulk goods (often on pallets ) from one type of transport receptacle to another.
To illegally touch the ball with the hand or arm.
examples: If the defender handballs in the penalty area, a penalty is awarded.

definitions.definition: To (legally) pass a football by holding it with one hand and hitting it with the other.
To insert a hand into someone's anus .

main_definition: ( transitive ) To manually load or unload a container , trailer , or to otherwise manually move bulk goods (often on pallets ) from one type of transport receptacle to another.
secondary_definitions: ( soccer ) To illegally touch the ball with the hand or arm.
( Australian rules football ) To (legally) pass a football by holding it with one hand and hitting it with the other.
( sexuality , slang ) To insert a hand into someone's anus .
